Reviellere has spent the majority of his career in France during two separate spells with Rennes and Lyon.

The defender amassed a total of 426  games during his 15 years in Ligue 1 and managed to score five goals.

Internationally, Reveillere represented France at the 2010 World Cup and Euro 2012. 

